FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our canine marketplace
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the dog marketplace work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our marketplace connects dog breeders and sellers with potential buyers. Users can browse listings, communicate with sellers, and arrange purchases or adoptions through our secure platform.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Are the dogs on your marketplace health-checked?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We require all sellers to provide up-to-date health certificates and vaccination records for their dogs. However, we always recommend that buyers arrange their own veterinary check-up before finalizing any purchase.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I list my dog for adoption on your marketplace?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! Our marketplace supports both sales and adoptions. You can create a listing for your dog and specify that it's for adoption rather than sale.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How do you ensure the safety and well-being of the dogs?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: We have strict guidelines for sellers regarding the care and treatment of dogs. We also encourage buyers to report any concerns, and we investigate all reports thoroughly. Any sellers found to be mistreating animals are immediately removed from our platform.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What breeds of dogs can I find on your marketplace?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Our marketplace features a wide variety of dog breeds, from popular breeds like Labrador Retrievers and German Shepherds to rarer breeds. You can use our search filters to find specific breeds or browse through all available listings.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Dog Marketplace
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the dog marketplace work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our dog marketplace connects reputable breeders and rescue organizations with potential dog owners. You can browse available dogs, filter by breed, age, and location, and contact sellers directly through our platform.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Are the dogs on your marketplace health-checked?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, all dogs listed on our marketplace must have up-to-date health certificates and vaccinations. We work closely with breeders and rescues to ensure the well-being of all dogs.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I meet a dog before making a purchase?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Absolutely! We encourage potential owners to meet dogs in person before finalizing any adoption or purchase. Our platform facilitates safe meet-and-greets between buyers and sellers.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: What if I have issues with my dog after purchase?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We offer a 14-day guarantee on all dogs. If you experience any health issues or compatibility problems, please contact us immediately. We'll work with you and the seller to find the best solution.
